<h3 id="EdiNieTex">Editions of Nietzsche&rsquo;s Texts</h3>

<p>
The following editions of Nietzsche&rsquo;s works have been
referenced. Translations are the author&rsquo;s own.</p>

<dl class="sentag tag4em">
<dt>[KGA]</dt>
<dd><em>Werke: kritische Gesamtausgabe</em>, 40 volumes, Colli,
